name: Frozen
description: Artist: Vida V. | I drew a single almond shaped line, and with it I made a petal, and from the petal a layer of petals, all in TwoToJazz. Then I bent and overlaid many such layers into a flower, and colored it using material from my other TwoToJazz pieces. TwoToJazz is an iPad creativity app developed by Vida | Creation date: January 25, 2015
